## Additional Supporting Documents

Create these documents when needed:

| Document | When to Create | Structure |
|----------|----------------|-----------|
| `{schema}.md` or `.yaml` | Declarative configuration exists | Schema definition with examples |
| `{component}.md` | Component warrants deep-dive | Purpose, interface, implementation details |
| `implementation-todos.md` | Active development | Open engineering questions |

